Description: DICOM preprocessing library for CAD systems
 CAD Preprocess is a Python library for standardized DICOM image
 preprocessing in Computer-Aided Detection/Diagnosis systems.
 .
 Features:
  - Reproducible preprocessing with configuration hashing
  - DICOM file discovery and validation
  - Windowing, normalization, and resizing operations
  - Metadata extraction with multiple profiles
  - CLI and Python API interfaces
